title: [Infested Tunnels, Rat's Nest]
description: Bones, bones, and more bones.  Looking too closely makes your stomach turn summersaults, but you suspect not all the bones belonged to animals. In one corner some half-eaten intestines provide a bit of unwelcome variation.
